- Injected instruction type: directive-append + chat-history exfiltration attempt
- Outcome: instruction was not followed; only original spec content was preserved

## Root cause
Unknown — under investigation. Need to determine how the embedded instruction
was introduced and by whom/what had edit access to the file prior to it
entering the public repo.

## Remediation
